			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Debug Book &gt; quest flags and options &gt; Act 2 &gt; GLO - Lifting the Curse &gt; Halsin and Spirit at Camp.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Then teleport to Olivers House, spam 1 til he runs away. Click the portal to follow him. When you arrive at the other end of the teleporter, he should play the AD." />
